  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libxkbcommon</title>

    <para>
      <application>libxkbcommon</application> is a keymap compiler and
      support library which processes a reduced subset of keymaps as
      defined by the XKB specification.
    </para>

    &lfs130_checked;

